{"tid":127974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓大使話死者唔係金正男 促兩國聯合調查","createTime":"2017-02-20T12:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T12:55:01.000Z","uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce3c9271715ea23c3fc7f4fa984c3ee95c30a83","tid":127974,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"金正男在馬來西亞遭毒殺事件，演變成大馬與北韓的外交爭議。北韓駐馬國大使指，大馬當局的調查有政治動機而且不可信，堅稱死者並非金正男，要求雙方聯合調查；而大馬首相納吉就反駁，沒必要去抹黑或中傷北韓，強調調查會客觀地進行。<br />\n<br />\n北韓駐馬國大使康哲（Kang Chol），今早被大馬傳召以表明金正男遺體處理的立場。他之後稱北韓目前只確認事件中有一名持北韓護照、名為金哲（Kim Chol）的男子的死訊，堅稱死者並非金正男，與大馬當局的說法不符。<br />\n康哲又指：「事發已經七天了，但仍未有明確證據去證實死因，現階段來說我們不能相信大馬警察的調查。」有報道指康哲認為大馬的調查帶有政治動機，提出要由雙方聯合調查求真相。<br />\n北韓早前曾要求領回遺體但被拒，駐馬大使康哲上周五發表聲明數落大馬政府，指摘「馬來西亞與敵對勢力勾結，企圖欺騙我方」，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時表明北韓反對解剖死者遺體，要求大馬進行火葬。</span><br />\n路透社/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170220/56328931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170220%2F56328931&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e329e86f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170220%2F56328931&h=fefd7b33\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170220/56328931</a><br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n幾時叫真金正男出黎講幾句啊金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afcee291ed2e1369ac1ac8843333c5292a8322c","tid":127974,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:50:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b4242b81010d1e7923e719881b5a1c908f267e2","tid":127974,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/photo/bkncn-20170217103659782-0217_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170217122448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170217%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170217103659782-0217_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170217122448&h=557ce9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真金正男咪係度囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705865673e016cdc8e6a32c9bf3db679ec68372f","tid":127974,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/photo/bkncn-20170217103659782-0217_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170217122448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170217%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170217103659782-0217_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170217122448&h=557ce9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真金正男咪係度囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}